imdb.plot outline: Join us as we explore the ultimate expression of man's cooperation with nature. Turning water, soil, sunshine and seed into a bounty, responsible for feeding the 7 billion humans and countless animals that call earth home, is no easy task. But, five farmers have accepted the challenge. This is their story.
